{"tid":850801,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"Jusco而家啲懶高級食店好似唔錯","createTime":"2018-10-06T17:08:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T19:03:05.000Z","uid":111088,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fe5970fd8a22ba6cc5a231848c769670610cc5ed","tid":850801,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T17:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/005939_bd2c5c982a7bbc9c80d6c47dd65ef89f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F005939_bd2c5c982a7bbc9c80d6c47dd65ef89f.jpg&h=b304d98a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/005942_c574a6edaf3d4217fabf29f604beaf59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F005942_c574a6edaf3d4217fabf29f604beaf59.jpg&h=911b59b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/005945_31493d7262d3f3978478fcfb5a8b9802.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F005945_31493d7262d3f3978478fcfb5a8b9802.jpg&h=6950d3bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/005947_26a8aac924da890009d4a601aafeb5b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F005947_26a8aac924da890009d4a601aafeb5b7.jpg&h=87839463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/005950_cd11174f2d9186a49501d1812a7b2539.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F005950_cd11174f2d9186a49501d1812a7b2539.jpg&h=222386e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/005952_d0c7a39f4b9bf83b6108f10826869f18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F005952_d0c7a39f4b9bf83b6108f10826869f18.jpg&h=2924d485&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/005955_66f4c6526702b0575e42f848bd187725.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F005955_66f4c6526702b0575e42f848bd187725.jpg&h=1bd40d14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/005957_5a8a91b5d79e0b67e053ce44a5908494.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F005957_5a8a91b5d79e0b67e053ce44a5908494.jpg&h=d2b03810&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/010001_062424961b014cf652240ca2434cae70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F010001_062424961b014cf652240ca2434cae70.jpg&h=bf3130a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/010003_96113a14a36ed73945c0bdcaf5de5f5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F010003_96113a14a36ed73945c0bdcaf5de5f5a.jpg&h=faed76f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當然啦唔好expect佢天上有地下無<br />\n亦都知道食左一半租<br />\n但係呢間貴撚<br />\n貴得嚟都算係咁<br />\n食材尚算高質同埋最少新鮮<br />\n其他野有得呃但係海膽呃唔到人<br />\n真係好樣唔腥同埋識溶嘅<br />\n個油甘魚骹我覺得個皮唔夠脆但係個魚油都幾香<br />\n然後我知食三文魚係不智但係食落口感同油香都唔差<br />\n甲殼燒細佬我第一次食<br />\n印象唔差<br />\n最少所有野都係鮮唔係腥<br />\n個麵豉湯比較好笑<br />\n姐係佢掉鳩曬啲三文魚骨頭頭尾尾落去一齊煲<br />\n差鳩啲哽骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係麵豉冇過咸，成件事都有返個鮮味<br />\n個龍蝦好撚韌<br />\n個虎蝦就唔錯幾鮮味<br />\n嗰兩塊傻餅反而幾好食<br />\n夠脆又足料<br />\n圖中淺色係粟米深色係咖喱牛肉傻餅<br />\n個人覺得唔錯<br />\n雖然啲comment講完好似冇講咁<br />\n但係呢個年代想搵檔野入得口嘅都唔容易<br />\n入口係鮮唔係腥已經要感恩<br />\n唉。"},{"pid":"92f09b571a6704de47c2b351b9f1d69de4b899e3","tid":850801,"uid":65603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T17:28:23.000Z","msg":"幾錢"},{"pid":"785030f8addd674c71c97dc1f9875ed741b57453","tid":850801,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"92f09b571a6704de47c2b351b9f1d69de4b899e3","tid":850801,"uid":65603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T17:28:23.000Z","msg":"幾錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T17:51:02.000Z","msg":"呢度加埋都四百幾"},{"pid":"2fa0fc4a79d4d7ac4833475f9f668ec8cb00e507","tid":850801,"uid":67237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T18:06:07.000Z","msg":"好似同平時d放題差唔多?"},{"pid":"759aef09efafbcf14624aaa1e024ff7f6b76aeb4","tid":850801,"uid":199179,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T19:29:16.000Z","msg":"名?"},{"pid":"7c24f2b9e1b6c47e4b152618c77a9621b44e0af5","tid":850801,"uid":63172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T19:47:17.000Z","msg":"地址"},{"pid":"83cd44f68392d297627c7ccd93de853e95da074d","tid":850801,"uid":124116,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T19:50:19.000Z","msg":"康山 日文名食堂？<br />\n返工有幾個月日日都係果到食佢個魚生飯，次次佢都厚切，仲好多塊，係真唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c8f65afd3bbfd10d83a693cc2f2334e5034f24","tid":850801,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T20:01:31.000Z","msg":"地址？名？"},{"pid":"6edc87b2db5c2860b0160b32b2629d04148e1f96","tid":850801,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fa0fc4a79d4d7ac4833475f9f668ec8cb00e507","tid":850801,"uid":67237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T18:06:07.000Z","msg":"好似同平時d放題差唔多?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T01:26:56.000Z","msg":"幾個人食<br />\n除開一人百幾<br />\n睇你點睇"},{"pid":"23e6a0862c15f327230e982cbd88234a9d1f471c","tid":850801,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T01:27:15.000Z","msg":"地址唔開啦<br />\n廢事俾人話打手"},{"pid":"c5822555b9eda3653e2f769a99db08d0d1e26782","tid":850801,"uid":10652,"like":0,"dislik